data.description: Step into this beautiful three bedroom, two bath home nestled in the well established Enclave In The Woods neighborhood. This area is close to shopping, medical and personal services, as well as, convenient to major throughfares and quick access to all of San Antonio's most interesting attractions. Come home to a like-new retreat with a two car garage, large chef's kitchen, granite counter tops. contour ceilings, incredibly open floor plan and great flow for those who love to entertain. This beautiful home features a landscaped yard that is just the right size to be easily maintained. A covered front entry with a couple of dramatic steps and back covered patio welcome you to come inside. The  walk-in closet and beautiful, well equipped on-suit, with a separate water closet, and loads of "getting-ready" room stylishly complete the plush master package. This well cared for gem is a must see.
